  "text": "The proof is divided in three steps. Each step consists roughly in reducing the equivalence of theorem 3.1, by rewriting it in terms of different models of (∞, 1)-categories until we abut to a comparison problem of bisimplicial sets. We solve this problem by using an improved version of the homotopy invariance theorem of classification spaces obtained in [CITATION_1] .",
